{"lemma":"صَفِّ","slug":"صَفِّ","root":"ص.ف.ف","root_slug":"ص-ف-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ف-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صَفّ","root":"صفف","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24402","","n24406"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"row, line (sequence of people or objects)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"battle order (arrangement of soldiers in battle)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"setting in type"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"year, grade, form, rank"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"class"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to line up, align"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to compose, classify"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to park (a car)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Of the root ص ف ف (ṣ f f). Potentially an Aramaic borrowing, doublet of ضَفَّ (ḍaffa, “to push, to throng, to jam, to collect together”), the cognate of which is attested in the passive participle as Jewish Babylonian Aramaic צְפִיפ (ṣəp̄īp̄, “crowded, pushed into”), while the noun is also found as Jewish Babylonian Aramaic צַפָּא (ṣappā, “row”), a relative of which would be Jewish Palestinian Aramaic צפד (ṣfd, “to weave”), as this meaning is present in Arabic in an extended root Arabic ضَفَرَ (ḍafara, “to weave, to plait”), though the example of عَصًا (ʕaṣan) shows that rarely Proto-Semitic *ṣ́ inherited as Arabic ص (ṣ) is possible. Compare the suspicious term صَفَد (ṣafad, “fetter, shackle”), as well as رَفّ (raff, “shelf, a part of furniture where one rows things into”), and صُفَّة (ṣuffa, “bench”) is also a borrowing and possibly related to the root."},"ipa":["/sˤaff/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24402","headword_ar":"صَفَّ","root":"Sf","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~N","text_ar":"صَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stationed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, O, K,) a company of men, (S, M, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) in war (S, O, K) &c., (O, K,) and a military force, (TA,) and also [in a similar sense] a thing, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a rank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"row,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"line:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, O, K:) and likewise ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sf~f","text_ar":"صفّف","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSofiyfN","text_ar":"تَصْفِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IDrd, O, K, TA;) but this has an intensive signification. (IDrd, O, TA.) ―         -b2-  One says also of a she-camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSuf~u yadayohaA Einoda AlHalabi","text_ar":"تَصُفُّ يَدَيْهَا عِنْدَ الحَلَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She sets her fore legs evenly, side by side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"not putting one of them in advance of the other, as if about to go onward,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the occasion of being milked"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, M, O, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safana","text_ar":"صَفَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man: and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAna","text_ar":"صَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Swn","text_ar":"صون"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And [in like manner] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~ati AlA_ibilu qawaAy^imahaA","text_ar":"صَفَّتِ الاـِبِلُ قَوَايِمَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camels set their legs in an even row"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b3-  And of a she-camel one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSuf~u A^aqodaAHFA mino labanihaA A_i*aA Hulibato","text_ar":"تَصُفُّ اَقْدَاحًا مِنْ لَبَنِهَا اـِذَا حُلِبَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She yields a row of bowls of her milk when she is milked"},{"kind":"text","text":"], because of the abundance of her milk. (S, O, K *.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSuf~u bayona","text_ar":"تَصُفُّ بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miHolabayoni A^awo valaAvapK","text_ar":"مِحْلَبَيْنِ اَوْ ثَلَاثَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) or simply"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSuf~u","text_ar":"تَصُفُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She combines two milking-vessels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three, at one milking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, O; *)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~af~u","text_ar":"الصَّفُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning her"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being milked into two milking-vessels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to combine them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O. [In the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano taHoluba","text_ar":"اَنْ تَحْلُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano tuHolaba","text_ar":"اَنْ تُحْلَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And a rájiz, cited by AZ, says, referring to a she-camel,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"taSuf~u fiY valaAvapi AlmaHaAlibi"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She is milked into three milking-vessels at one milking"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) One says also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~ahaA","text_ar":"صَفَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HalabahaA Saf~FA","text_ar":"حَلَبَهَا صَفًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He milked her into two bowls,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three, at one milking;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into two bowls;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the pronoun referring to a she-camel]. (M. [One or the other of these two meanings appears to be indicated by what there precedes this.]) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suf~a","text_ar":"صُفَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Aljamori liyano$awiYa","text_ar":"عَلَى الجَمْرِ لِيَنْشَوِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) is said of flesh-meat (S) [app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was laid, cut into a strip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into strips, upon the live coals to broil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Al$~amosi liyajif~a","text_ar":"فِى الشَّمْسِ لِيَجِفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the sun to dry"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) for one says of him who has prepared flesh-meat cut into strips, or oblong pieces, and dried in the sun,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~a All~aHoma","text_ar":"صَفَّ اللَّحْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and [in like manner] one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~ahu EalaY Aln~aAri liyano$awiYa","text_ar":"صَفَّهُ عَلَى النَّارِ لِيَنْشَوِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~a All~aHoma","text_ar":"صَفَّ اللَّحْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~u","text_ar":"صَفُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he cut the flesh-meat into broad slices:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and accord. to ISh, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aSofiyfu","text_ar":"التَّصْفِيفُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~a$oriyHu","text_ar":"التَّشْرِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"a piece of flesh-meat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, so that it is translucent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in the present art:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AltSfyf","text_ar":"التصفيف"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a kind of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$oriyH","text_ar":"تَشْرِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the cutting"},{"kind":"text","text":"a piece of flesh-meat"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, so that it is translucent by reason of its thinness, and then throwing it upon the live coals."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$rH","text_ar":"شرح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiyfN","text_ar":"صَفِيفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  See also 8, in three places. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~a","text_ar":"صَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a bird, (M, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~N","text_ar":"صَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It extended its wings in a line,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it expanded its wings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K,) in the sky,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not move them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and struck"},{"kind":"text","text":"[an evident mistake for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not strike"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with them its sides like the pigeon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) such as do so are not to be eaten; (Msb, K;) as the vulture and the hawk: (Msb:) it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuw^okalu maA daf~a walaA yuw^okalu maA Saf~a","text_ar":"يُوْكَلُ مَا دَفَّ وَلَا يُوْكَلُ مَا صَفَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K, TA. See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"df","text_ar":"دف"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safafotu lils~aroji","text_ar":"صَفَفْتُ لِلسَّرْجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safafotu lils~aroji","text_ar":"صَفَفْتُ لِلسَّرْجِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suf~apF","text_ar":"صُفَّةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safafotu Als~aroja","text_ar":"صَفَفْتُ السَّرْجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, and so in one place in the O,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSofafotuhu","text_ar":"اَصْفَفْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) but this latter verb is of weak authority, (O,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I put to the horse's saddle a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suf~ap","text_ar":"صُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]: S, O, K, TA:) [and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~a Ald~aAb~apa","text_ar":"صَفَّ الدَّابَّةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~a lahaA","text_ar":"صَفَّ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made for the beast a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suf~ap","text_ar":"صُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n24406","headword_ar":"صَفٌّ","root":"Sf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rank, row,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"line"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of things]; (KL, PS;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an even"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sador","text_ar":"صَدْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of any things: (M:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a company of men standing in a rank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"row,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"line:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SufuwfN","text_ar":"صُفُوفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, O, Msb, K;) and the sing. may also be used in the sense of the pl.; it may be used either thus in the sense of the pl. or as a sing. in the Kur xviii. 46. (O.) Hence, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saw~uwA Sufuwfakumo","text_ar":"سَوُّوا صُفُوفَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Make even your ranks"},{"kind":"text","text":"] in prayer. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A station of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sufuwf","text_ar":"صُفُوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ranks of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSaf~N","text_ar":"مَصَفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And hence, (M,) as used in the Kur xx. 67,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSal~FY","text_ar":"مُصَلًّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of prayer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of prayer on the occasion of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiyd","text_ar":"عِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"festival"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Az, M, O;) because the people stand there in ranks: (M:) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place where people assemble for their"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eiyd","text_ar":"عِيد"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Az, O:) or, in that instance,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saf~FA","text_ar":"صَفًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"may mean"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muSoTaf~iyna","text_ar":"مُصْطَفِّينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standing in ranks"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Az, M, O,) as a denotative of state. (M.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pair of bowls"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qadaHaAni","text_ar":"قَدَحَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") [app., as seems to be indicated,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are filled at one milking of a camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; because they are put together. (M.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain medicament with which the teeth are whitened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.)"}],"source_refs":["M","O","K","Az"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}